 in stores from 1st June, and with its stylish design and budget-friendly price, we’re expecting it to sell out quickly.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you’ve got your eye on one, it’s worth acting fast. But if there’s no Lidl near you or you’re just browsing other bladeless fan options, we’ve included a couple of great alternatives below.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3 id=\"section-shop-alternative-bladeless-fans\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShop alternative bladeless fans\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv data-id=\"0b3f6ce7-f027-4a10-a2dd-1841d4ad0e77\"\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://www.awin1.com/awclick.php?awinmid=3769\u0026amp;awinaffid=103504\u0026amp;clickref=idealhome-gb-4171645264641853199\u0026amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dunelm.com%2Fproduct%2Frediffusion-bladeless-fan-1000247313%3FdefaultSkuId%3D30932586\" data-model-name=\"Rediffusion Bladeless Fan\" data-url=\"https://www.dunelm.com/product/rediffusion-bladeless-fan-1000247313?defaultSkuId=30932586\" target=\"_blank\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" rel=\"sponsored noopener\" data-hl-processed=\"hawklinks\" data-placeholder-url=\"https://www.awin1.com/awclick.php?awinmid=3769\u0026amp;awinaffid=103504\u0026amp;clickref=hawk-custom-tracking\u0026amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dunelm.com%2Fproduct%2Frediffusion-bladeless-fan-1000247313%3FdefaultSkuId%3D30932586\" data-google-interstitial=\"false\" data-merchant-name=\"Dunelm\" data-merchant-id=\"19895\" data-merchant-network=\"AW\" data-merchant-url=\"dunelm.com\"\u003e\u003cp data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/WPauzGngKqu9LLehUxsKM9-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/WPauzGngKqu9LLehUxsKM9-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/WPauzGngKqu9LLehUxsKM9-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/WPauzGngKqu9LLehUxsKM9-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/WPauzGngKqu9LLehUxsKM9-7